dev-custom-session.name: codenamegary/l4-lock
dev-custom-session.description: A Laravel 4 package to lock down a site and require a simple username/password BEFORE auth is executed. Useful for doing things like locking down a site so a client can test before going live while without interfering with auth and other stock framework options.
